              "text": "Perfect! Let's start with the intuition, then build up the math naturally. Imagine each neuron as a simple function that takes inputs, weighs them by importance, adds them up, and decides whether to 'fire' or not. The magic happens when thousands of these work together and learn from examples. Want me to show you a simple code example first?"
